    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>pasta </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the<strong> pasta </strong>for 7-9 min (10-12 min for wholewheat) or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>pasta</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/creamy-sausage-kale-and-lemon-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the pasta is cooking, reboil a kettle</p><p>Heat a very large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, squeeze your<strong> sausage meat</strong> from the skins into the pan (clean hands is the best way!), discard the skins</p><p>Break the <strong>sausage meat </strong>up into large, bite-sized pieces with a wooden spoon and cook for 6-7 min or until crispy and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/creamy-sausage-kale-and-lemon-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and chop your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> into wedges, then add to the pan to soften</p><p>While the onion and sausage meat are cooking, peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and your <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong> in 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><span class=\"text-purple\">[210ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[270ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/creamy-sausage-kale-and-lemon-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>shredded kale</strong>, then add to a colander over the sink and pour<strong> boiled water</strong> all over until it's bright green and wilted</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/creamy-sausage-kale-and-lemon-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the sausage meat is brown and crispy, reduce the heat to low</p><p>Add the<strong> sliced garlic</strong> and your<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken stock</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/creamy-sausage-kale-and-lemon-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> soft cheese</strong> and the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and stir it all together</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/creamy-sausage-kale-and-lemon-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained pasta </strong>and<strong> wilted kale</strong> to the pan with a splash of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until the sauce has thickened slightly and begins to stick to the pasta \u2013 this is your<strong> creamy sausage, kale & lemon pasta</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/creamy-sausage-kale-and-lemon-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy sausage, kale & lemon tortiglioni</strong> topped with the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Drizzle with some<strong> olive oil</strong>, season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and garnish with a<strong> lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
